data.description: Welcome to Edgewater, a water-accessible community!  Live like you’re on vacation year-round! This charming cottage features a new 2022 HVAC system, 3 bedrooms, 2  updated bathrooms, luxury vinyl tiled floors in the living/dining area, and a lovely yard with a deck and shed.    The location is superb with a short walk to Woodland Beach, less than a mile to Edgewater Elementary School, and a short drive to shopping and dining.   This community is a commuter's dream with easy access to RT-2, I-97, and R-50.  See you at our Open House this Sunday, 10/22 from 1-4!
